            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Daniel.4:1-37",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDaniel%204%3A1-37%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_1%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDaniel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ENebuchadnezzar%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Dream%20about%20a%20Tree%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Verses%204%3A1-3%20are%20numbered%203%3A31-33%20in%20Aramaic%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3EKing%20Nebuchadnezzar%20sent%20this%20message%20to%20the%20people%20of%20every%20race%20and%20nation%20and%20language%20throughout%20the%20world%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BPeace%20and%20prosperity%20to%20you!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_2%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20want%20you%20all%20to%20know%20about%20the%20miraculous%20signs%20and%20wonders%20the%20Most%20High%20God%20has%20performed%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_3%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EHow%20great%20are%20his%20signs%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Ehow%20powerful%20his%20wonders!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1%22%3EHis%20kingdom%20will%20last%20forever%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Ehis%20rule%20through%20all%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_4%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Verses%204%3A4-37%20are%20numbered%204%3A1-34%20in%20Aramaic%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%2C%20Nebuchadnezzar%2C%20was%20living%20in%20my%20palace%20in%20comfort%20and%20prosperity.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_5%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20one%20night%20I%20had%20a%20dream%20that%20frightened%20me%3B%20I%20saw%20visions%20that%20terrified%20me%20as%20I%20lay%20in%20my%20bed.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_6%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20issued%20an%20order%20calling%20in%20all%20the%20wise%20men%20of%20Babylon%2C%20so%20they%20could%20tell%20me%20what%20my%20dream%20meant.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_7%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20all%20the%20magicians%2C%20enchanters%2C%20astrologers%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EChaldeans.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20fortune-tellers%20came%20in%2C%20I%20told%20them%20the%20dream%2C%20but%20they%20could%20not%20tell%20me%20what%20it%20meant.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_8%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20last%20Daniel%20came%20in%20before%20me%2C%20and%20I%20told%20him%20the%20dream.%20(He%20was%20named%20Belteshazzar%20after%20my%20god%2C%20and%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20holy%20gods%20is%20in%20him.)%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_9%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20said%20to%20him%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BBelteshazzar%2C%20chief%20of%20the%20magicians%2C%20I%20know%20that%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20holy%20gods%20is%20in%20you%20and%20that%20no%20mystery%20is%20too%20great%20for%20you%20to%20solve.%20Now%20tell%20me%20what%20my%20dream%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_10%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BWhile%20I%20was%20lying%20in%20my%20bed%2C%20this%20is%20what%20I%20dreamed.%20I%20saw%20a%20large%20tree%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20earth.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_11%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20tree%20grew%20very%20tall%20and%20strong%2C%20reaching%20high%20into%20the%20heavens%20for%20all%20the%20world%20to%20see.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_12%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20had%20fresh%20green%20leaves%2C%20and%20it%20was%20loaded%20with%20fruit%20for%20all%20to%20eat.%20Wild%20animals%20lived%20in%20its%20shade%2C%20and%20birds%20nested%20in%20its%20branches.%20All%20the%20world%20was%20fed%20from%20this%20tree.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_13%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BThen%20as%20I%20lay%20there%20dreaming%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20messenger%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Aramaic%20%3Cem%3Ea%20watcher%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%204%3A23.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20a%20holy%20one%2C%20coming%20down%20from%20heaven.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_14%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20messenger%20shouted%2C%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BCut%20down%20the%20tree%20and%20lop%20off%20its%20branches!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3EShake%20off%20its%20leaves%20and%20scatter%20its%20fruit!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1%22%3EChase%20the%20wild%20animals%20from%20its%20shade%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20birds%20from%20its%20branches.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_15%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20leave%20the%20stump%20and%20the%20roots%20in%20the%20ground%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Ebound%20with%20a%20band%20of%20iron%20and%20bronze%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Eand%20surrounded%20by%20tender%20grass.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1%22%3ENow%20let%20him%20be%20drenched%20with%20the%20dew%20of%20heaven%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Eand%20let%20him%20live%20with%20the%20wild%20animals%20among%20the%20plants%20of%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_16%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20seven%20periods%20of%20time%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Elet%20him%20have%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20wild%20animal%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Einstead%20of%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_17%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20this%20has%20been%20decreed%20by%20the%20messengers%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A17%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Aramaic%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20watchers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Eit%20is%20commanded%20by%20the%20holy%20ones%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1%22%3Eso%20that%20everyone%20may%20know%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Ethat%20the%20Most%20High%20rules%20over%20the%20kingdoms%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet1%22%3EHe%20gives%20them%20to%20anyone%20he%20chooses%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-poet2%22%3Eeven%20to%20the%20lowliest%20of%20people.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_18%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BBelteshazzar%2C%20that%20was%20the%20dream%20that%20I%2C%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar%2C%20had.%20Now%20tell%20me%20what%20it%20means%2C%20for%20none%20of%20the%20wise%20men%20of%20my%20kingdom%20can%20do%20so.%20But%20you%20can%20tell%20me%20because%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20holy%20gods%20is%20in%20you.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_19%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDaniel%20Explains%20the%20Dream%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BUpon%20hearing%20this%2C%20Daniel%20(also%20known%20as%20Belteshazzar)%20was%20overcome%20for%20a%20time%2C%20frightened%20by%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20dream.%20Then%20the%20king%20said%20to%20him%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BBelteshazzar%2C%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20alarmed%20by%20the%20dream%20and%20what%20it%20means.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BBelteshazzar%20replied%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20wish%20the%20events%20foreshadowed%20in%20this%20dream%20would%20happen%20to%20your%20enemies%2C%20my%20lord%2C%20and%20not%20to%20you!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_20%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20tree%20you%20saw%20was%20growing%20very%20tall%20and%20strong%2C%20reaching%20high%20into%20the%20heavens%20for%20all%20the%20world%20to%20see.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_21%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20had%20fresh%20green%20leaves%20and%20was%20loaded%20with%20fruit%20for%20all%20to%20eat.%20Wild%20animals%20lived%20in%20its%20shade%2C%20and%20birds%20nested%20in%20its%20branches.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_22%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThat%20tree%2C%20Your%20Majesty%2C%20is%20you.%20For%20you%20have%20grown%20strong%20and%20great%3B%20your%20greatness%20reaches%20up%20to%20heaven%2C%20and%20your%20rule%20to%20the%20ends%20of%20the%20earth.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_4_23%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BThen%20you%20saw%20a%20messenger%2C%20a%20holy%20one%2C%20coming%20down%20from%20heaven%20and%20saying%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BCut%20down%20the%20tree%20and%20destroy%20it.%20But%20leave%20the%20stump%20and%20the%20roots%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20bound%20with%20a%20band%20of%20iron%20and%20bronze%20and%20surrounded%20by%20tender%20grass.%20Let%20him%20be%20drenched%20with%20the%20dew%20of%20heaven.%20Let%20him%20live%20with%20the%20animals%20of%20the%20field%20for%20seven%20periods%20of%20time.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_